flawed and has racial patterns. And that's

1180
01:06:37.972 --> 01:06:41.852
why we think that when you feed that data and more data,

1181
01:06:42.292 --> 01:06:46.112
AI will use past data and those patterns

1182
01:06:46.192 --> 01:06:50.072
to formulate the results that it will, and that may

1183
01:06:50.152 --> 01:06:50.712
result to

1184
01:06:51.572 --> 01:06:52.552
